Amplify-DNS

# 

<span key="3a11f5a582c34d1aa9ca5448a153e1eb"><span offset-key="3a11f5a582c34d1aa9ca5448a153e1eb:0">Amplify DNS</span></span>

## 

<span key="b9c3b80b0864408b983da98a111f8e25"><span offset-key="b9c3b80b0864408b983da98a111f8e25:0">Configuring your subdomain</span></span>

<span key="140d6f7071b740049a6ba7984818e64b"><span offset-key="140d6f7071b740049a6ba7984818e64b:0">When your application is deployed to Amplify, you'll get an automatically generated URL that you can use to open the site in your browser. This is handy for doing a quick test, but not very useful otherwise. You want to get a proper domain, like </span>`https://c.bridgestoprosperity.dev`</span>

<span key="d9a8ea1d83df46caaba7d0330de6661a"><span offset-key="d9a8ea1d83df46caaba7d0330de6661a:0">The basic flow for hooking a proper domain name up to your application is as follows:</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="3201f86687fc4053a38ad4f1b7451ecf"><span offset-key="3201f86687fc4053a38ad4f1b7451ecf:0">Click 'Domain Management'</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="2cc2f4ac11894543ae729e3e699cfabc"><span offset-key="2cc2f4ac11894543ae729e3e699cfabc:0">Click 'Add Domain'</span></span>

3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
    <span key="58cdd67855234d9a80ffd556c2d5f258"><span offset-key="58cdd67855234d9a80ffd556c2d5f258:0">You should see your product domain in the dropdown when you search for domain.</span></span>

    -   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

        <span key="d87dbd67f15f4815a900ff45d3c72990"><span offset-key="d87dbd67f15f4815a900ff45d3c72990:0">If not, please contact your APL.</span></span>

4.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">4.</span>
    <span key="a6b1841844d944cf8c1e9227a01403ab"><span offset-key="a6b1841844d944cf8c1e9227a01403ab:0">Choose your product domain</span></span>

5.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">5.</span>
    <span key="96642a75dfb642aa90dff8fe6ce95261"><span offset-key="96642a75dfb642aa90dff8fe6ce95261:0">Add the front-end subdomain per the Labs Engineering Standards</span></span>

    -   <img src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," class="r-1nf4jbm" />

        <span key="a60b57972a6f4a7b88aa82f7bfd2ea67"><span offset-key="a60b57972a6f4a7b88aa82f7bfd2ea67:0">For example </span>`c.bridgestoprosperity.dev`</span>

6.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">6.</span>
    <span key="5cca991a3e984db297096857732977bc"><span offset-key="5cca991a3e984db297096857732977bc:0">Click 'Configure Domain'</span></span>

7.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">7.</span>
    <span key="8546ece9155a4618a1ed405f58af97d1"><span offset-key="8546ece9155a4618a1ed405f58af97d1:0">Press 'Remove' next to the </span>`www`<span offset-key="8546ece9155a4618a1ed405f58af97d1:2"> subdomain line</span></span>

8.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">8.</span>
    <span key="63568e75937e48b0b2885f8b7b6a2889"><span offset-key="63568e75937e48b0b2885f8b7b6a2889:0">Uncheck the 'Setup redirect from...\` option</span></span>

9.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">9.</span>
    <span key="75b06deb647447c1b23982c67a4c733e"><span offset-key="75b06deb647447c1b23982c67a4c733e:0">Save</span></span>
